cross: Cymbidium Hazel Tyers 'Santa Maria' x Cymbidium Satin Dragon 'Cinnabar'

measurements.description: Eleven full round flowers on one 76-cm inflorescence; sepals and petals white, blushed burgundy, burgundy speckles striated longitudinally; lip white, wide dark burgundy band distally, bugundy spots side lobes; column white overlaid burgundy, ventral surface spotted burgundy, anther cap cream; substance firm; texture matte.
